<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-13-0259 </DOCNO><TEXT>This is a guide for evaluating and implementing cogeneration projectsin North Carolina. It emphasizes economic assessment and describes cogenerationtechnologies and legal guidelines. Included are hypothetical projectsto illustrate tax and cash flow calculations and a discussion of cogeneration/utilitysystem interconnection. In addition, the manual contains utility rateschedules and regulations, sources of financing, equipment information,and consulting assistance.</TEXT></DOC>